43","tid":835941,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"54bee4f8411900e0073487f0736f9f1dd4fe8676","tid":835941,"uid":130568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0bc29364b0aaeb4c426fe06120d59658d330cc06","tid":835941,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:08:10.000Z","msg":"表示PS4已步入產品周期的末段"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:27:04.000Z","msg":"「稍早時間Sony曾表示PS4已「步入產品周期的最後階段」（entered the end of its lifecycle），大家都以為明年甚至今年就會公佈PS5時，Sony今日（5月24日）就出來派定心丸：我們需要3年左右的時間來部署PS5。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:28:26.000Z","msg":"3年時間由2016年開始計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:30:41.000Z","msg":"篇野2018-05-24架<br />\n<br />\n今個星期二（5月22日）Sony社長吉田憲一郎在Sony的企業策略會議上，表示PS4已步入產品周期的末段；而過往PlayStation的產品周期一般都在6至7年，現在還愈來愈短，2013年推出的PS4按慣例來說也確實是進入後期了。而Sony Interactive Entertainment的CEO小寺剛（John Kodera）今日接受華爾街日報訪問時透露，「將會用3年的時間來部署我們的下一步，現在蹲下是為了將來可以跳得更高」（We will use the next three years to prepare the next step, to crouch down so that we can jump higher in the future）<br />\n<br />\n想引戰就開過另一個Post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a05147bb6acc377ceedbab01086a2771e7f2b73","tid":835941,"uid":16515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:31:17.000Z","msg":"等PS10啦"},{"pid":"00cbf4abc21fb2429af7707eaf96119a5f701652","tid":835941,"uid":58089,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:48:03.000Z","msg":"幾弱智既人先會問...."},{"pid":"35795f7e6eff447e1ce15d8490f04ce193dad8cc","tid":835941,"uid":70964,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00cbf4abc21fb2429af7707eaf96119a5f701652","tid":835941,"uid":58089,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:4